00:00:17.300 --> 00:00:20.980
Today, she speaks with us about her latest
book "Ingenious",

00:00:20.980 --> 00:00:24.240
and it brings lessons from her teaching, and
research into creativity

00:00:24.240 --> 00:00:26.690
and shows how anyone can increase their creative
genius

00:00:26.690 --> 00:00:27.840
