00:00:31.100 --> 00:00:33.460
at Stanford, both for myself and the many
other folks

00:00:33.460 --> 00:00:35.610
who have been through her class.

00:00:35.610 --> 00:00:39.760
Her courses on creativity impact not only
engineers, and D school grads,

00:00:39.760 --> 00:00:45.020
but lawyers, doctors, um public health advocates,
